Facilitates typing french special characters on german keyboards in Windows following the corresponding shortcuts from macOS. Tested only on Windows 10.

Make sure Windows' default shortcut Alt+Shift (change Keyboard layout) is deactivated by doing this: https://superuser.com/questions/698037/can-i-disable-the-altshift-shortcut-to-change-language-in-windows-8-1-or-win#698595
